sources.description:
After a few years of financial hardship, a young mother (RACHEL) decides to go back to work to help her ex-husband with the mounting bills. With no one to watch their 4-year-old daughter (MIA), the mother decides to enroll her into the local daycare center called Little Ones owned by a seemingly responsible older woman, (DEBORAH). After a few weeks of Mia's awkward behavior, Rachel concludes her daughter may be getting mistreated by (GABBY) one of the centers daycare teachers.

2014.  Stars: Kayla Ewell, Christy Carlson Romano, Bryce Johnson
